        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-8">
          Turning business intent into systems that execute.
        </p>
        <a href="#layers" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
